{"tid":1450323,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"1人1 Post: 5星旗，做乜都啱！","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:38:28.000Z","uid":73504,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"71b5b89b2ec6293daf7927702e37cc2b6109917b","tid":1450323,"uid":73504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:30:27.000Z","msg":"5星旗，做乜都啱！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家將呢個Post Copy再重新開新Post，等多啲人知</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">林鄭重用4點鐘許sir 招數，相信理由好簡單，大家都知道，<span style=\"color: red;\">係要制造示威者暴力升級既假象，殺錯良民</span><br />\n<br />\n我亦相信大家都知道，佢地既目標客戶唔係我地，<span style=\"color: red;\">而係中間偏黃同淺藍既人</span><br />\n<br />\n依堆人好易被形式主義洗腦，<span style=\"color: red;\">淨係接收到單一資訊，比如今日大肚婆穿羊水入唔到醫院就夠入腦<br />\n</span><br />\n所以避免重2014年既覆轍，我地必用八奇之思考領域，<span style=\"color: red;\">避免林鄭扣今次運動同港獨為同一帽子<br />\n</span><br />\n所以，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新既方向為愛國愛港，落實一國兩制，立刻實行雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由於<span style=\"color: red;\">d廢老淨係識接單一而含有象徵意義既畫面，所以tvb所拍到既示威場面，包gear , 頭巾，旗咩都好，</span>都要有五星旗<br />\n<br />\n有幾個好處：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 衝擊可以繼續升級，又唔驚cctvb 抹黑，因為廢老淨係識認五星旗，有5星做乜都得<br />\n<br />\n2. 而可以塞住口交部把口<br />\n<br />\n3. 可以輸出革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位手足，快d支持我地祖國偉大既淘寶，去剷除亂中既香港政府</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jqqkOsW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjqqkOsW.png&h=24cdc970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家要學會共產黨統戰精髓<br />\n統戰 = 統一戰綫，聯合次要敵人，打擊主要敵人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">將呢次鎮壓行動打造成 中聯辦/梁振英/何君堯/鄧炳強 等江派勢力搞亂香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">名正則言順</span></span><br />\n<br />\n遊行打愛國旗號，唔好搞習近平肖像，因爲習派係拉攏對象<br />\n因爲無論你想唔想，所有5大訴求最終話事人其實係佢<br />\n吸引班淺藍加入，然後起碼等班深藍廢佬出少句聲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">對家用Divide and rule，我地就要增加朋友/減少敵人+孤立對手</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"ebde659e782f6042370fe94eed2da83c0abd57d2","tid":1450323,"uid":73504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:37:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"938f37c2ddfd2fddf17e599caf17fda57dc4c84f","tid":1450323,"uid":73504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:36:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[red<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/</span>red]</span>"},{"pid":"aa3dccde229ca56457a9d947f79cce52266e7ee9","tid":1450323,"uid":73504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"7681f6e30ea6c009e58e6ae34a58a1ecf00e7eda","tid":1450323,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"放核彈都唔割,但係你要我認做中國人就割到你老母都唔認得"}]}